dct_alternative_sm: Gulf of Pohai (Chihli) Rocky Point (Kinshan Tsui) to Temple Head (Hwanhaiszeti Tsui)
dct_description_sm: From British and French surveys to 1934 with additions from other sources.
Depths shown by soundings and tints; relief by form lines.
Shows low water areas, drainage, railways, roads, buildings.
